			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Gary Byler, GOP 2nd District Chairman, played Secret Santa today to many children in need of winter coats.  Byler paid the balances due on all layaways for children&#8217;s coats at Burlington Coat Factory in Virginia Beach.</p>
<blockquote><p>Byler wrote a check for $1,136.82 on Thursday. At the Burlington Coat Factory’s Military Highway store, which has $3,000 in childrens’ coats on layaway, Byler said he’ll match the first $1,000 donated.</p></blockquote>
<p>Read the story in the <a href="http://hamptonroads.com/2008/12/beach-lawyer-pays-childrens-coats-layaway-store">Virginian-Pilot.</a></p>
