<p>Easy tools and capabilities are out there to figure it out and use it.  Cheap/free options are available.</p>
<p>Q: How do you communicate securely internally? A: <a href="http://groups.google.com">Google Groups</a> is a good way to do it.</p>
<p>A copy of his PowerPoint presentation will be sent to Jeff Frederick to pass along to others.</p>
